  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposal, by reason of its size, scale, and positioning, represents an overly large and obtrusive extension that fails to be subordinate to the host dwelling and the overall size of the plot. Furthermore, the extension overshadows the remaining, limited garden space. The extension, therefore, fails to respect the character of the wider terrace and fails to meet policies LP1 (&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: justify; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Design Quality and Local Character)  and LP17 (Housing design) of&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;The Hackney Local Plan (2020) and policies D3 (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-8b61408f-7fff-6c0e-1ea3-cd3afb6a0581&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Optimising site capacity through the design-led approach&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;) and D4 (Delivering good design) of The London Plan (2021) and the Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009).&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-17241562-7fff-2227-cc61-d167b21203cc&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed development, by reason of its size, bulk, and location, has the potential to significantly reduce the light and outlook for adjoining occupiers to the north and west and have an overbearing impact. Without a BRE Sunlight and Daylight Assessment, the LPA is unable to conclude otherwise, and the proposal, therefore, fails to meet policy LP2 (Development and Amenity) of the Hackney Local Plan (2020) and policy D6 (&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: justify; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Housing quality and standards) &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;of the London Plan (2021) and Hackney&#x27;s Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-afae4a41-7fff-a3d6-f31c-051f2ff20378&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
  ],
